{"type": "article", "id": 18030, "title": "磁吸牙刷", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-25T06:50:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135733NYn40c23l6tOdmrI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一根可以悬挂在墙面的牙刷，在“X”符号里藏有一块磁铁，刚好吸在带磁性的墙贴上。如果是没有吸铁物品，比如牙膏，则可使用带吸铁的夹子，悬挂在旁边，让他们成为墙面的装饰。墙贴经过多种测试，并不会受潮湿环境的干扰，与牙刷一起有多种颜色搭配，给单调的浴室多一份色彩。<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/shennbrush/shenn-toothbrush\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135730XyP43hODemdNUbrS.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68380952\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135731yEqrzQa2DJG5egw7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135731KAe0YUaJyn1utQPM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135732FUIMYl0k4eWsix75.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48529412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135732AoPFODxqM03yrT5l.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}